name: POWERSKULL_03 - Scarlet Telepathy Cranium
description:
Master Alchemists of an ancient tribe from the extinct planet 396-Gamma were responsible for crafting the POWERSKULLZ.

The Legends from the Great Elders describe how this  Scarlet Telepathy Cranium gave the ability to communicate telepathically to whoever grasped it with both hands and elevated it to eye level.

This artefact would only work when handled by a human. The skull's resonant frequency is in tune with the electromagnetic field emanated by humans. The POWERSKULL would eliminate the barrier that separates the skull bearer's thoughts and the thoughts of other living beings. The human carrying the Scarlet Telepathy Cranium would obtain the permanent ability to communicate with any living being across any distance using only the mind.

Other living forms' magnetic fields would not be tuned to the Transmutational Healing Cranium and would not activate it.

The POWERSKULLZ are part of the POWERVERSE, a reality where humans have achieved their highest potential and live as gods.
